Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.96,0:41:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在的宇宙正在扩张{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Right now the universe is expanding.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.29,0:41:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们测量到的重力{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And the force of gravity as we measure{\r}
