Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.58,0:41:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在过去的20年 我们才认识到暗能量{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}It's only been the last 20 years that we've even known that dark energy{\r}
