Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.22,0:42:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}在那种情况下 宇宙会经历一次非常高温的热死亡{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}In that case, the universe will experience a really hot heat-death,{\r}
