Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.63,0:42:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}温度很高{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}High temperatures.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.90,0:42:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}恒星走向毁灭 行星走向毁灭{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Stars get destroyed, planets get destroyed.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.76,0:42:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}只剩下一个不同与往的 死气沉沉的宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You get a different form of a lifeless universe...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.47,0:42:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}一个以高温代替极冻的宇宙{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}One which is hot instead of in the deep freeze.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.27,0:42:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}但是 它不会形成"遮阳幕"{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Still, don't break out the sunscreen yet.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.37,0:42:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我敢打赌 宇宙会最终成为非常低温的极冻世界{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}My bet is that the universe will end up in a very low temperature deep freeze...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.75,0:42:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为目前的暗能量 看起来或许会{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Because it seems that the current dark energy might be the type{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.47,0:42:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}继续加速宇宙的扩张 永不停止{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}that will continue to accelerate the expansion forever.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.31,0:42:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}假如果真如此 宇宙的温度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}If that's the case, the temperature of the universe{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.11,0:43:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}会反复接近绝对零度这一终极寒冷的温度{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}will become arbitrarily close to absolute zero... The ultimate deep freeze.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.79,0:43:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}寒冷是我们宇宙的一个决定性因素{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Cold is a critical ingredient of our universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.88,0:43:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}它是我们所见到的宇宙的必要组成{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Cold is essential to having the universe that we see.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.24,0:43:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因为如果没有寒冷 能量就不会流动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}Because without a cold spot, energy doesn't flow.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.74,0:43:18.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你需要能量从热流向冷{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}You need energy to flow from hot to cold.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.13,0:43:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}正是能量的流动{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And it is the flow of energy that leads to{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.70,0:43:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}才形成现在的宇宙万物 包括我们人类本身{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}all the structures that we see in the universe, including ourselves.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.23,0:43:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}所以 如果没有能量通过各种可能方式{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So we wouldn't be here if energy weren't trying to flow{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.79,0:43:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}竭力从热的地方流向宇宙各处{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}from hot concentrated organized places{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.26,0:43:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}我们就不会在这里存在{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}into the many forms that it can flow into in the universe.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.54,0:43:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}因此 日后感到冬日的寒冷或是被雪球打中的时候{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}So the next time you feel a winter chill or get hit with a snowball,{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.77,0:43:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}你要记住--如果不是寒冷 你就不会在这里{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}just remember-- If it weren't for cold, you wouldn't be here.{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.08,0:43:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}而且 如果算是一丝安慰的话{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}And if it's any consolation, you won't be around{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.70,0:43:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}现在的你不用花上几百个数万亿年{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}hundreds of trillions of years from now when the universe{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.30,0:43:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}去陪同宇宙迎接最后的极冻结局{\r}\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&\blur3}enters its final state of deep freeze.{\r}
